BT 1 0 0 1 0 62.2 Tm /F1 10.3 Tf 14.5 TL .514993 Tw (The Sunrise Medical Center Code Blue team consists of the on-call Hospitalist or Intensivist \(team leader\),) Tj T* 0 Tw 1.615621 Tw (an ICU or ED nurse \(medication nurse\), a Respiratory Therapist \(airway management\), a second nurse) Tj T* 0 Tw 7.410267 Tw (\(compressions/documentation\), Pharmacy \(on radio standby\), and Security \(crowd and family) Tj T* 0 Tw .625075 Tw (management\). Response time target is under 3 minutes from activation to bedside arrival for all core team) Tj T* 0 Tw (members.) Tj T* ET
